---
title: Spanish Style Cod & Chips with Olives and Vine Tomato
description: We love a good Spanish  'fish and chips' and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/spanish-style-cod-chips-78434780-169c13a0.jpg
